            . This shawl was brought to be pawned with me on the evening of the 14th of July; I thought it was like one which I knew my aunt had; part of my mother's house had been burnt down in the great fire, and the shawl was taken from it.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18150913-67-person626">
                  ROBERT 
                  COOMBS
               <interp inst="t18150913-67-person626" type="surname" value="COOMBS"></interp>
