                     <interp inst="t18150913-67-person626" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am an officer. I produce the shawl. The prisoner told me, that on the night of the fire a gentleman and lady whose house had been burned down, came to his house, and asked for a night's lodging, which they had, and not being able to get change for a ten-pound note in the morning, they left this shawl.</p>
